(20, 1, '2010-09-23 22:11:52', '2010-09-23 22:11:52', 'This web site has been prepared by David Read, for informational purposes only. It is not intended as advertising, although in some jurisdictions this web site may be considered advertising. David Read has made a fair effort to comply with all known legal and ethical requirements while creating this web site.\r\n\r\nNothing herein is intended as legal advice nor should you rely upon any information in these web pages as a source of legal advice and there is no implied guarantee that this information is correct, complete, or up-to-date. Receipt of any such information by you does not create an attorney-client relationship between you and David Read or the law firm of Strong and Hanni. Unless you are a current client of David Read or the law firm of Strong &amp; Hanni P.C., please do not send any confidential information by email or through this website. If you are not a current client and you send an email to David Read or an individual at Strong &amp; Hanni P.C., you acknowledge that we have no obligation to maintain the confidentiality of any information you submit to us, unless we have already agreed to represent you or we later agree to do so. Thus, David Read or an attorney at the law firm of Strong and Hanni may represent a party adverse to you, even if the information you submit to us could be used against you in a legal matter, and even if you submitted it in a good faith effort to retain us.\r\n<h3>Blog Disclaimer</h3>\r\nThis blog is written for the information and education of its readers only. It should not be construed as legal advice and is not intended to create an attorney-client relationship. Given the general nature of this blog, no one should act on its contents without seeking independent legal advice. <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Any comments or questions posted on the website are public and therefore nothing on this website can be construed as confidential or privileged.</span>', 'Disclaimer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'disclaimer', '', '', '2011-04-29 21:42:32', '2011-04-29 21:42:32', '', 0, 'http://clients.edit.com/801divorce/draft6/', 110, 'page', '', 0),
