(26, 1, '2010-09-23 22:12:35', '2010-09-23 22:12:35', '<h1>Schedule a Consultation with Utah''s Family Law Team</h1>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: small;">Consulting with a lawyer before you decide to hire one is always a good idea. Meeting with one of the firm‘s family law attorneys, face to face, will demonstrate how the firm might handle your case.</span></span>\r\n\r\nFill out the form below, or call: 801-Divorce (348-6723) to schedule your consultation.  If you are considering legal action for a family law matter in the State of Utah, we recommend that you consult with an attorney who will help you understand your rights and options according to Utah law.\r\n\r\nWe are licensed attorneys to serve clients throughout the State of Utah.\r\n\r\n<em><strong>DISCLAIMER</strong></em><em>: No attorney - client relationship will be created by virtue of information, facts or questions you provide by submitting this form. The general information given in this website is intended to be a starting point only by describing general aspects of the law, and it is important that you consult with an attorney with regard to your specific legal rights.</em>', 'Schedule a Consultation', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'schedule-a-consultation', '', '', '2011-05-24 23:06:18', '2011-05-24 23:06:18', '', 0, 'http://clients.edit.com/801divorce/draft6/', 80, 'page', '', 0),
