(230, 1, '2011-04-27 21:15:59', '2011-04-27 21:15:59', 'Mediation is a form of alternative dispute resolution.  The law firm of Strong and Hanni has trained lawyer mediators in the firm who act as a neutral to aid parties and their attorneys in settling their disputes without the need for court intervention.  Mediation saves the parties the cost of litigation as well as the time delays that the formal court process usually causes.  The firm’s lawyers not only act as mediators, but also represent parties in mediations.\r\n\r\nPlease call 801-Divorce (348-6723) for more information.', 'Mediation', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mediation', '', '', '2011-04-27 21:44:02', '2011-04-27 21:44:02', '', 14, 'http://clients.edit.com/801divorce/draft6/?page_id=230', 130, 'page', '', 0),
(225, 1, '2011-04-27 21:13:37', '2011-04-27 21:13:37', 'A Legal Separation is an agreement between parties who remain married but are no longer going to live together and who want to define their legal obligations and responsibilities to each other and to their children.  These agreements provide the roadmap for the parties’ financial future and their relationship with their children.  They must be thoroughly and carefully done by lawyers with experience in negotiating and drafting such agreements.  Attorneys at the law firm of Strong and Hanni spend a portion of their time doing just that.\r\n\r\nPlease call 801-Divorce (348-6723) for more information.', 'Legal Separation', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'legal-separation', '', '', '2011-04-27 21:43:11', '2011-04-27 21:43:11', '', 14, 'http://clients.edit.com/801divorce/draft6/?page_id=225', 110, 'page', '', 0),
