(216, 1, '2011-04-27 21:05:22', '2011-04-27 21:05:22', 'The law firm of Strong and Hanni has lawyers that are particularly skilled in the preparation and prosecution of complex financial and custody matters.  Although we do not promote litigation for litigation’s sake, trial skill is an important talent to have if efforts at settlement fail.  Our family law attorneys were trained and certified in trial advocacy at the National Institute of Trial Advocacy (NITA).\r\n\r\nPlease call 801-Divorce (348-6723) for more information.', 'Litigation in Trial Courts', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'litigation-in-trial-courts', '', '', '2011-04-27 21:42:03', '2011-04-27 21:42:03', '', 14, 'http://clients.edit.com/801divorce/draft6/?page_id=216', 80, 'page', '', 0),
