(344, 1, '2011-04-27 20:02:54', '2011-04-27 20:02:54', 'We work hard to help people. As you can tell from looking through our website, we want you to be informed.  We want you to make smart choices. Very few people are happy at the end of the divorce process, but hopefully our clients understand the process, why we made the choices we did, and feel confident in the results.\r\n\r\nOur focus is to keep your focus on what’s important. By doing that, you’ll not only save money but you’ll also get better results. We know how hard it can be to focus on reasonable objectives in highly emotional cases, but it can be done as you make positive and informed choices.\r\n\r\nFamily law is a hard choice for a lawyer, given the high degree of conflict and the emotions involved. But we have chosen this field of law because we know we can make a difference, in a very personal and real way, for countless people and their kids. We feel good about the job we do because every day, we make that difference.', 'The Firm', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-32', '', '', '2011-04-27 20:02:54', '2011-04-27 20:02:54', '', 2, 'http://clients.edit.com/801divorce/draft6/2011/04/27/2-revision-32/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
